      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not just social anxiety though. it's like they've already decided who i am. i've seen the group chats, i've seen the memes. even if i talk to a therapist, they'll just tell me it's in my head, but it's not. it's everything. i'm just so tired of fighting to exist in a world that clearly doesn't want me here. it feels like everything is just... loud and hateful and there's no way out.",
